  <summary date="2019-01-03T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Federal Employee Retroactive Pay Fairness Act

This bill requires federal employees and District of Columbia public employees furloughed due to a lapse in appropriations that begins on or&#160;about December 22, 2018, to be compensated at their standard rate of compensation for the period of such lapse as soon as practicable after such lapse ends.</summary>
